member.summary:
Gets or sets a white list of characters.
If it is not null and not empty, OCR recognizes only the white-listed characters.

[C#]
OcrEngine ocr = new OcrEngine();
ocr.Config.Whitelist = new char[] {'1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8', '9', '0'};

